  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2d24c81&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AqEYA4tnIPqgwD0lMVp4YrLz80fZtkDlThoe17iaWS2t6CoezqicGsxYwoL461BKLR38IHoficmREcg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit;\">大家好，我是袋鼠帝</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31djn\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个多月前写了一篇<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwMzE4NjU5NA==&amp;mid=2247512469&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c4542bafe29361cd21ad9bce238bc9e2&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"批量扒抖音爆款&amp;自动二创\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">批量扒抖音爆款&amp;自动二创</a>的教程内容，没想到深受大家喜欢</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5138888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 333px;height: 171px;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029680\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b99e768b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1D8aPnjKafE5BbnQBwYRnqdATCUtSNHabqXTxDhQuf7OKsUGYNxj7cxddnRXT5AVZ1mZmLKVw9vTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a318su\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当时又给自己挖了个坑，立了个flag... 居然达成了🤦‍♂️</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.17592592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029681\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e53ad22d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D8aPnjKafE5BbnQBwYRnqdnlmMpPoX1hAZeQY3KRziakmiaI8CypbibawUooknYCHdU1IBEAqKamoZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3gnp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没想到，大家对这块需求还挺旺盛的，评论区很多小伙伴也在呼吁出小红书篇。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkggs3lg1np9\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-template-id=\"771\" data-mpa-category=\"模板\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div data-mpa-category=\"模板\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;grid-column-gap: 7px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8490740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029682\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8725a52c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D8aPnjKafE5BbnQBwYRnqdhubcJJTNYpe25JMCW8VF4UicVZluds9iadAZufmFZD1O2qdOzLaIzZRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.85\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029683\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf529cc4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D8aPnjKafE5BbnQBwYRnqdugLesmJpr1D9IWMbpFFZzSicTg10Diabl4bgUq3RAQ2lr1IP3MLoJMCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a313yc\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">抱歉，鸽了很久，今天批量扒小红书爆款&amp;批量自动二创，它来了！</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a320we\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面是一个真实需求</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3651226158038147\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"734\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029685\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd75ae3d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3VzV5fiau1QnLe41cEr73I4ialGqOExyC5dT0icSqfhjibNlXP2iaXFSdjgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3q9x\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf6yscs41h\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">今天这篇所讲的方案（不止一个方案），基本能实现这个需求的核心点了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a390i\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf6yscs41h\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">建议收藏，并转发给你身边有需要的朋友，如果觉得有帮助，别忘了三连😄（对我来说非常重要）</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31z5d\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先拆解一下这个需求：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3y6k\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">1.抓取指定的小红书账号内容，筛选爆款；</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a319z0\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">2.结合产品知识库，用LLM拆解爆款结构，并进行二创；</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3zjl\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">3.接到第三方AI服务进一步处理（比如生成视频切片）。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a322kh\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">这是一套基于小红书的批量爆款二创工作流</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5581395348837209\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2752\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029687\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fa59551a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3PUCXSZ3GY9YNt2vt8ossv25u5c671ftibj0D1zBREibYdg677pJgpLWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkjtugs81vxy\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">「飞书小红书插件工坊」</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3z34\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">第一步，</span>抓取小红书指定账号的内容：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31oy\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">其实飞书多维表格就有个现成的免费插件。一个多月前我在X上分享过，叫小红书插件工坊</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3x0q\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://pam9ocg47ka.feishu.cn/base/extension/replit_3066a388517de3e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://pam9ocg47ka.feishu.cn/base/extension/replit_3066a388517de3e5</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjt6hdc1b0y\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkjt6hds290\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">大家可以关注一下我的X账号（袋鼠帝），更新更频繁，会发一些新玩意儿，一些感悟，一些公众号没有的信息。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100029688\" data-ratio=\"1.1171477079796266\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1178\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67cccc84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3f4Jz0icNcL4y4q3kIxgsnfC6WsGPGvjGmOYeuSqomcEds9YQse3U7ww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgo9n0m17zf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3cox\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">然</span><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">后巧的是，X上的大佬@</span><span leaf=\"\">派大鑫</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">，给我安利了他们做的小红书采集浏览器插件，体验下来也非常不错（这个后面会说）</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.52079866888519