1jvw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">这个飞书插件怎么用呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31rsm\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有两个核心参数需要配置一下：小红书cookie、多维表格授权码</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31dxp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">多维表格授权码获取方式很简单，就两步，点两下就能获取成功，插件自带获取指引，这里就不赘述了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8734693877551021\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"980\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029693\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37f1b797&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3Wk4TxYzf7nBBG1nJnLdrYMH2L0xZH6U6awPicLeZTO111CUnlw6bp4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31t96\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">小红书cookie获取方式（方法很多，仅供参考）：</span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk783q19jq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a324jn\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk78xnp26\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">先打开小红书网页端，然后按下&nbsp;</span><b data-path-to-node=\"17,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">F12</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">&nbsp;打开开发者工具，点击&nbsp;</span><b data-path-to-node=\"17,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"18\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">Network (网络)</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">&nbsp;选项卡，可以在搜索栏随便输入一个关键词，回车</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk783q19jq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3ajh\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk78xnp26\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">随便过滤一个带keyword的API请求，在header里面就能找到cookie了</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5645833333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2880\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029692\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef6c0c7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3lsBMbtZSZMssJ1ELMa8tybsGdz94dXGooBQsP3j2MGJOJicNCvZwA0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk783q19jq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3223v\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk78xnp26\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">我们先来测试一下获取指定博主的笔记（以我的小红书「袋鼠帝」为例）</span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk783q19jq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3z0s\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgk78xnp26\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">由于我的小红书笔记图片太多了（好多都是公众号链接直接转长文），获取得有点慢，就不全部放出来了</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3133m\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">另外我测试了关键词搜索，但会报cookie错误...估计是这块功能暂时还有bug吧</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3cv1\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过第一步指定博主抓取已经完成了</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a315o3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">飞书多维表格有定时执行的功能，理论上开启定时执行就可以实现自动了，不过看了下，暂时还不支持自动执行插件功能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6288\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2500\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029698\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=207aaee5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud305v6ozKibSOOgqR56siaNm21Y3Fm6nNVa9A0llJu8SZjpwHt6kCpNEWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31mnd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接着，我们可以增加一个AI字段，让AI帮我们根据获取的信息批量筛选爆款。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.425357873210634\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"978\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029699\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5152cb64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3UBQVosFZklSFGohFkGpibSbicx4zZ2TjxknmY5ict4S9xkNvNB8mChGWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a317je\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">为了更一目了然，我们可以再创建一个分类字段来对结果进行分类，也更方便触发后续的自动化流程</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5204545454545455\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"880\" style=\"width: 338px;height: 514px;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a9bee55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3JY4DhhqpNv9hxSGQkIosFkG8Yic4s81y5qibN6Gl1NNc4MG1Cat8AQyQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3m2z\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">比如需要根据产品知识库进行二次创作，就可以新建一个自动化流程，条件就是新增的「是否二创」字段值为是 才触发，下图右边的触发操作可以选择API。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31b8f\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">可以事先在Fastgpt搭建产品知识库，并打造一个可以结合产品知识、小红书爆款进行二创的Agent。下面图右侧要接入的就是这个Agent的API。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029701\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee6c3d31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3f03F4lnoQ5wop9zrk6skl3txGm3z3UicZ8u53nibiatrdU0uVnlRLGZlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a37f4\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">二创完成之后，可以再回写到多维表格的字段中</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31rxy\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">整个自动化流程大概像这样（见视频，下面例子跑通了流程，没有实现具体业务）：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3bmp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当「二次创作」字段值为是，触发流程，调用fastgpt上预设号的Agent，完成二创，回写到「二创结果」字段中。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31np8\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">第三步，调用第三方API服务进一步处理（比如生成视频切片），操作也是跟上面自动化流程类似。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3q3l\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">今天这篇主要是授人以渔，我相信聪明的你，稍微花点时间，一定能举一反三，运用到实际业务中。</span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkjtt5v0229r\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">「小红书浏览器插件」</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a323ww\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">接下来我们再看看文章开头提到的朋友：@派大鑫开发的「小红书浏览器插件」</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31fe5\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">在Chrome商店直接搜索<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">「好采助手」</span>即可，点击「添加至chrome」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029706\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=974bcdb8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3G8A9exQppn7q8c7ibx0AeYlsXpgIrfbwvdBVaqZ04sDYbTKO94jyl3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjttp3z1btd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkjttp4bsds\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">并且该插件即将支持除了小红书以外的平台采集</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100029707\" data-ratio=\"0.3861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f04f7ee4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3sktZr2SPWtlFfSEmYJNIpZSszPHP18EtefoVNsqsvFprQo9KeSDRNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a38q9\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">支持把笔记详情下载到本地，或者导入Eagle、同步到飞书</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9695290858725761\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"722\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029714\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f422640e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1AqEYA4tnIPqgwD0lMVp4Yr5lGXFoKKRibpNzTVFrKEyrpHcgGLSP2rgOD8fU1fAobfXzEecEictUrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a315vo\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">同步到飞书需要去飞书开放平台，创建一个应用，然后获取应用的App ID、App Secret，填写到好采助手</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31hsc\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">应用需要添加上多维表格的操作权限，并发布。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100029708\" data-ratio=\"0.45740740740740743\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb1cdd80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3STm7TfNKQCU2fmNQMq2Sic8NZVZLYg3ibDowGMCqVCRCAVialrKMTtWbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31ls1\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">另外还需要在好采助手里面添加一个多维表格链接。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3ixm\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">复制网页端打开的多维表格的链接</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.462037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029709\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71df1a59&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DlvNibe6ibianwLO9o9o33ud3K4OH0vowwdibQYzAib2C5QWWQ5NPprAzDMy7SOpSPklCqt0ORXV0AagA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31sxj\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">到这一步如果直接就去测试同步飞书，大概率会报一个错：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029715\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da32e086&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1AqEYA4tnIPqgwD0lMVp4YrkDFWmuT7gsibficrKWyNic0CfWxLc9IicWCJ97ViaRTojeSFUbVJa6uNX6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a32e1\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是因为没有把你新创建的飞书多维表格跟飞书应用绑定</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31j9j\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我们还差最后一步操作（把应用和新建的飞书多维表格关联）：</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31vxj\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后看演示效果，不仅可以抓图文，也可以抓视频，非常方便。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a322il\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">适合边刷小红书的时候边收集素材</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3aum\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghcpk0oxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">我觉得，飞书多维表格的插件，加上好采助手这个浏览器插件，可以配合起来用，一种是大范围的同步，AI筛选（更泛），一种是人工筛选然后同步（更精准）</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3fgu\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">PS：好采助手，本质上是调用了飞书的API。免费用户，一个月的飞书API调用量限制在10000次，次月刷新，升级套餐之后是无限制。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a3fgu\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">飞书多维表格官方学习文档：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjvx8lt9xw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkjvx8mc1w6n\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><a href=\"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/category/6933474572494716956-%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/category/6933474572494716956-%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkjsy9a31lrn\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">看完≠学会，大家一定要思考+实践</span></span></p>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"mkj